      <p>
        <s>The movie <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="title">The Hate U Give</ref>, directed by <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="director">George Tillmann Jr.</ref>, was published in <date>2018</date>.</s>
        <s>In the given sequence of the film, <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Starr</ref> and her boyfriend <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Chris</ref> met in school and <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Chris</ref> excuses for the other day, where he did something, that made <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Starr</ref> angry.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>At the beginning of the given sequence, <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Chris</ref> walks on the school floor in <choice><orig>slowmotion</orig><reg>slow motion</reg></choice> and he shakes many <choice><orig>peoples</orig><reg>people's</reg></choice> hands and greets them, until he goes to <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character"><choice><orig>Starrs</orig><reg>Starr's</reg></choice></ref> locker and see her there.</s>
        <s><ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Starr</ref> is angry from the other day, where <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Chris</ref> gave her a condome.</s>
        <s><ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Chris</ref> says to <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Starr</ref> that he made a beat for her and shows it to her.</s>
        <s>She wasn't really impressed about it until <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Chris</ref> started to dance with the beat.</s>
        <s><ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Starr</ref> laughs and goes with <ref target="b10gk1_1" type="character">Chris</ref> away.</s>
      </p>
